Template.owningImplementationGuideName: Alberta Transcribed Reports CDA Implementation Guide
Template.title: CA-AB Transcribed Reports
Template.Description: This section describes constraints that apply to the header for all documents within the scope of this implementation guide. Header constraints specific to each document type are described in the appropriate document-specific section below.

Constraint.NarrativeText: SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="DOCCLIN" (CodeSystem: HL7ActClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 STATIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-1.2).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" (CodeSystem: ActMood urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001) (CONF:CONF-TR-1.3).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] realmCode="AB" (CodeSystem: HL7Realm urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1124 STATIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-1.4).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] typeId (CONF:CONF-TR-1.5).
This typeId SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.1.3" (CONF:CONF-TR-1.5a).
This typeId SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @extension="POCD_HD000040" (CONF:CONF-TR-1.5b).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId="2.16.840.1.113883.3.163.10.2.2" (CONF:CONF-TR-1.6).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id (CONF:CONF-TR-1.7).
This id SHALL be a globally unique identifier for the document
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code with @xsi:type="CV", where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet AlbertaTranscribedReportType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.392 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-1.8).
This code SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @nullFlavor="OTH" (CodeSystem: HL7NullFlavor urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1008) (CONF:2216-112).
This code SHALL specify the particular kind of document (e.g. History and Physical, Discharge Summary, Progress Note)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] title (CONF:CONF-TR-1.9).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] effectiveTime (CONF:CONF-TR-1.10).
This effectiveTime SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @value (CONF:CONF-TR-1.10a).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] confidentialityCode, where the code SHALL be selected from CodeSystem ConfidentialityCode (urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.25) STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-1.11).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] languageCode="en-CA" English Canadian (CodeSystem: ISO 639-3 urn:oid:1.0.639.3 STATIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-1.12).
SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] setId (CONF:CONF-TR-1.13).
SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] versionNumber (CONF:CONF-TR-1.14).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] recordTarget (CONF:CONF-TR-10.1).
This recordTarget SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="RCT" Record Target (CodeSystem: HL7ParticipationType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.90) (CONF:CONF-TR-10.2).
This recordTarget SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @contextControlCode="OP" Overriding Propagating (CodeSystem: HL7 Context Control Code urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1057) (CONF:CONF-TR-10.3).
This recordTarget SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] patientRole (CONF:CONF-TR-10.4).
This patientRole SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="PAT" Patient (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-10.5).
This patientRole SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id (CONF:CONF-TR-10.6).
This patientRole SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-10.7).
This patientRole SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-10.8).
This patientRole SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] patient (CONF:2216-9).
This patient SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="PSN" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:2216-152).
This patient SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:2216-153).
This patient SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] name (CONF:CONF-TR-10.11).
This name SHALL NOT contain [0..0] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-126).

This patient SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] administrativeGenderCode, where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet Administrative Gender (HL7 V3) urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.1 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-10.12).
This patient SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] birthTime (CONF:CONF-TR-10.13).
This patient SHALL NOT contain [0..0] maritalStatusCode, where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet Marital Status urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.12212 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-10.14).
This patient SHALL NOT contain [0..0] religiousAffiliationCode (CONF:CONF-TR-10.15).
This patient SHALL NOT contain [0..0] raceCode (CONF:CONF-TR-10.16).
This patient SHOULD contain zero or more [0..*] languageCommunication (CONF:2216-18).
The languageCommunication, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] languageCode, which SHALL be selected from ValueSet HumanLanguage urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.51 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-10.18).

The languageCommunication, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] modeCode, where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet LanguageAbilityMode urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.324 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-10.19).

The languageCommunication, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] proficiencyLevelCode, where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet LanguageAbilityProficiency urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.325 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-10.20).
The languageCommunication, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] preferenceInd (CONF:CONF-TR-20.21).
SHALL contain at least one [1..*] author (CONF:CONF-TR-3.1).
Such authors MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-401).
Such authors SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="AUT" Author (CodeSystem: HL7ParticipationType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.90) (CONF:CONF-TR-3.2).
Such authors SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @contextControlCode="OP" (CodeSystem: HL7 Context Control Code urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1057) (CONF:CONF-TR-3.3).
Such authors SHALL NOT contain [0..0] functionCode, where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet ParticipationFunction urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.87 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-3.5).
Such authors SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] time (CONF:CONF-TR-3.4).
This time MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @value (CONF:2216-203).
Such authors SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] assignedAuthor (CONF:2216-30).
This assignedAuthor SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ASSIGNED" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-3.6).
This assignedAuthor SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id (CONF:CONF-TR-3.7).
This id MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-196).
This assignedAuthor SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-3.8).
This assignedAuthor SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-3.9).
This assignedAuthor SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] assignedPerson (CONF:CONF-TR-3.10).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="PSN" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-3.11).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-3.12).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] name (CONF:CONF-TR-3.13).
This assignedAuthor SHALL NOT contain [0..0] assignedAuthoringDevice (CONF:CONF-TR-3.14).
SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] dataEnterer (CONF:CONF-TR-5.1).
The dataEnterer, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="ENT" Transcriptionist (CodeSystem: HL7ParticipationType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.90) (CONF:CONF-TR-5.2).

The dataEnterer, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @contextControlCode="OP" Overriding Propagating (CodeSystem: HL7 Context Control Code urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1057) (CONF:CONF-TR-5.3).
The dataEnterer, if present, SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] time (CONF:CONF-TR-5.4).
The dataEnterer, if present, SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] assignedEntity (CONF:CONF-TR-5.5).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] @classCode="ASSIGNED" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-5.6).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id (CONF:CONF-TR-5.7).
This id SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @nullFlavor="UNK" (CodeSystem: HL7NullFlavor urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1008) (CONF:2216-174).

The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] code with @xsi:type="CV", where the code SHALL be selected from CodeSystem RoleCode (urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.111) STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-5.8).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-5.9).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-5.10).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] assignedPerson (CONF:CONF-TR-5.11).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="PSN" Person (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-5.12).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-5.13).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] name (CONF:CONF-TR-5.14).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] informant (CONF:CONF-TR-7.1).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] custodian (CONF:CONF-TR-4.1).
This custodian MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-404).
This custodian SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="CST" (CodeSystem: HL7ParticipationType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.90) (CONF:CONF-TR-4.2).
This custodian SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] assignedCustodian (CONF:CONF-TR-4.3).
This assignedCustodian MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-215).
This assignedCustodian SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ASSIGNED" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-4.4).
This assignedCustodian SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] representedCustodianOrganization (CONF:CONF-TR-4.5).
This representedCustodianOrganization MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-402).
This representedCustodianOrganization SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ORG" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-4.6).
This representedCustodianOrganization SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-4.7).
This representedCustodianOrganization SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id (CONF:CONF-TR-4.8).
This id SHALL contain [0..0] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-208).
This representedCustodianOrganization SHALL NOT contain [0..0] name (CONF:CONF-TR-4.9).
This representedCustodianOrganization SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-4.10).
This representedCustodianOrganization SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-4.11).
SHALL contain zero or more [0..*] informationRecipient (CONF:CONF-TR-8.1).
The informationRecipient, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode (ValueSet: x_InformationRecipient urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.19366 STATIC) (CONF:2216-235).
The informationRecipient, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] intendedRecipient (CONF:CONF-TR-8.3).
This intendedRecipient SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ASSIGNED" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-8.4).
This intendedRecipient SHALL NOT contain [0..0] id (CONF:CONF-TR-8.5).
This intendedRecipient SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-8.8).
This intendedRecipient SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-8.9).
This intendedRecipient SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] informationRecipient (CONF:CONF-TR-8.10).
The informationRecipient, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="PSN" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-8.11).
The informationRecipient, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-8.12).
The informationRecipient, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] name (CONF:CONF-TR-8.13).
This intendedRecipient SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] receivedOrganization (CONF:CONF-TR-8.14).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ORG" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-8.15).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-8.16).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id (CONF:CONF-TR-8.17).
This id MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-224).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] name (CONF:CONF-TR-8.18).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-8.19).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain zero or one [0..1] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-8.20).
The receivedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] standardIndustryClassCode (CONF:CONF-TR-8.21).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] legalAuthenticator (CONF:CONF-TR-9.1).
MAY contain zero or one [0..1] authenticator (CONF:CONF-TR-2.1).
The authenticator, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="AUTHEN" (CONF:CONF-TR-2.2).
The authenticator, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] time (CONF:CONF-TR-2.3).
This time MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-405).
The authenticator, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] signatureCode="NA" nullFlavor (CodeSystem: Participationsignature urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.89 STATIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-2.4).
This signatureCode MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor="NA" (CodeSystem: HL7NullFlavor urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1008) (CONF:2216-270).
The authenticator, if present, SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] assignedEntity (CONF:CONF-TR-2.5).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ASSIGNED" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-2.6).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] id="UNK" (CodeSystem: HL7NullFlavor urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1008 STATIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-2.7).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] code, which SHALL be selected from CodeSystem RoleCode (urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.111) STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-2.8).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-2.9).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-2.10).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] assignedPerson (CONF:CONF-TR-2.11).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="PSN" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-2.12).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-2.13).
This assignedPerson SHALL contain at least one [1..*] name (CONF:CONF-TR-2.14).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] representedOrganization (CONF:CONF-TR-2.15).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] participant (CONF:CONF-TR-6.1).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] inFulfillmentOf (CONF:CONF-TR-14.1).
SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] documentationOf (CONF:CONF-TR-13.1).
The documentationOf, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="DOC" Documentation Of (CodeSystem: HL7ActRelationshipType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1002) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.2).
The documentationOf, if present, SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] serviceEvent (CONF:CONF-TR-13.3).
This serviceEvent SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ACT" Act (CodeSystem: HL7ActClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 STATIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.4).
This serviceEvent SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: ActMood urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.5).
This serviceEvent SHALL NOT contain [0..0] id (CONF:CONF-TR-13.6).
This serviceEvent SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code with @xsi:type="CV", where the code SHALL be selected from CodeSystem ActCode (urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.4) STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-13.7).
This code MAY contain zero or one [0..1] @nullFlavor (CONF:2216-339).
This serviceEvent SHALL NOT contain [0..0] effectiveTime (CONF:CONF-TR-13.8).
This serviceEvent SHALL NOT contain [0..0] performer (CONF:CONF-TR-13.9).
The performer, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] functionCode, where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet ParticipationFunction urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.87 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-13.11).
The performer, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] time (CONF:CONF-TR-13.12).
The performer, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] assignedEntity (CONF:CONF-TR-13.13).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] @classCode="ASSIGNED" (CodeSystem: RoleClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.110) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.14).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] id (CONF:CONF-TR-13.15).

The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] code with @xsi:type="CV", where the code SHALL be selected from ValueSet ProviderRoleCode urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.2.20.3.265 STATIC (CONF:CONF-TR-13.16).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-13.17).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-13.18).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] assignedPerson (CONF:CONF-TR-13.19).
The assignedPerson, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] @classCode="PSN" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.20).
The assignedPerson, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.21).
The assignedPerson, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] name (CONF:CONF-TR-13.22).
The assignedEntity, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] representedOrganization (CONF:CONF-TR-13.23).
The representedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] @classCode="ORG" (CodeSystem: EntityClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.41) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.24).
The representedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] @determinerCode="INSTANCE" (CodeSystem: EntityDeterminer urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.30) (CONF:CONF-TR-13.25).
The representedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] id (CONF:CONF-TR-13.26).
The representedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] name (CONF:CONF-TR-13.27).
The representedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] telecom (CONF:CONF-TR-13.30).
The representedOrganization, if present, SHALL NOT contain [0..0] addr (CONF:CONF-TR-13.28).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] relatedDocument (CONF:CONF-TR-12.1).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] authorization (CONF:CONF-TR-15.1).
SHALL NOT contain [0..0] componentOf (CONF:CONF-TR-16.1).
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] component (CONF:CONF-TR-17.1).
This component SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @typeCode="COMP" Component (CodeSystem: HL7ActRelationshipType urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1002) (CONF:CONF-TR-17.2).
This component SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @contextConductionInd="TRUE" (CONF:CONF-TR-17.3).
This component SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] nonXMLBody (CONF:CONF-TR-17.5).
This nonXMLBody SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="DOCBODY" Document Body (CodeSystem: HL7ActClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.6) (CONF:CONF-TR-17.6).
This nonXMLBody SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: ActMood urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001) (CONF:CONF-TR-17.7).
This nonXMLBody SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] text (CONF:CONF-TR-17.8).
This nonXMLBody SHALL contain zero or one [0..1] confidentialityCode (CodeSystem: ConfidentialityCode urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.25) (CONF:CONF-TR-17.9).
This nonXMLBody MAY contain zero or one [0..1] languageCode (CodeSystem: ISO 639-3 urn:oid:1.0.639.3 DYNAMIC) (CONF:CONF-TR-17.10).
